<br>
I usually have (ON A PERFECT PULL) one to one and a half bars of mana left, without harvesting. Sometimes its been to the point where I had to use my PoG robe to kill off the last mob because I was truly OOM. <br>
<br>
With good equipment and no screwups, id say 56 would be the min, but id prob go for 57 because of your new aoe.<br>
<br>
Otters are badasses, they come sowed, and speeded. Shellfish adds are more then annoying, they can quite easily stun you and get 4 speeded warriors on you very quickly, as well as passing aggro to the chief... who I have YET to not die from after aggroing.<br>
<br>
For pulling / hps reasons I would wait until 57.. do wyverns or raptors at 54.<br>
They take about 7 of my 940ish dmg aoes to kill.... even more with resists. <p><Fontsize=5><font color=red><b>Fediel T'Avar</b></font></font><br><fontsize=4><font color=red><b>58 Gnome Wizard</b></font></font><br><font color=red><b>Dark Breed Of Norrath<b></font><br><fontsize=4><font color=red>Wizard Officer</font></font></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showMessage?topicID=129.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showMessage?topicID=114.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.emailToFriend?topicID=97.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.threadControl?topicID=97.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=97.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=97.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graff